column3: This library allows typing ligatures and extra letters that are found in languages written with the Latin alphabet.

column1: *C1?OZ‖~palatalnasal‖SI‖En‖{U+0272}‖latin small letter n with left hook (U+0272)
*C1?OZ‖~capitalpalatalnasal‖SI‖En‖{U+019D}‖latin capital letter n with left hook (U+019D)
*C1?OZ‖~tcomma‖SI‖En‖{U+021B}‖latin small letter t with comma below (U+021B)
*C1?OZ‖~tcommacapital‖SI‖En‖{U+021A}‖latin capital letter t with comma below (U+021A)
*C1?OZ‖~capitaltcomma‖SI‖En‖{U+021A}‖latin capital letter t with comma below (U+021A)
*C1?OZ‖~scomma‖SI‖En‖{U+0219}‖latin small letter s with comma below (U+0219)
*C1?OZ‖~scommacapital‖SI‖En‖{U+0218}‖latin capital letter s with comma below (U+0218)
*C1?OZ‖~capitalscomma‖SI‖En‖{U+0218}‖latin capital letter s with comma below (U+0218)
